originalSql:
WITH RankedMovies AS (
    SELECT 
        t.id AS movie_id,
        t.title,
        t.production_year,
        COUNT(DISTINCT c.person_id) AS cast_count,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT a.name, ', ') AS actors_list
    FROM 
        title t
    JOIN 
        complete_cast cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id
    JOIN 
        cast_info c ON cc.subject_id = c.id
    JOIN 
        aka_name a ON c.person_id = a.person_id
    WHERE 
        t.production_year >= 2000
    GROUP BY 
        t.id, t.title, t.production_year
), MovieKeywords AS (
    SELECT 
        mk.movie_id,
        STRING_AGG(k.keyword, ', ') AS keywords_list
    FROM 
        movie_keyword mk
    JOIN 
        keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id
    GROUP BY 
        mk.movie_id
), FinalReport AS (
    SELECT 
        rm.movie_id,
        rm.title,
        rm.production_year,
        rm.cast_count,
        rm.actors_list,
        mk.keywords_list
    FROM 
        RankedMovies rm
    LEFT JOIN 
        MovieKeywords mk ON rm.movie_id = mk.movie_id
    ORDER BY 
        rm.production_year DESC, rm.cast_count DESC
)
SELECT 
    movie_id,
    title,
    production_year,
    cast_count,
    actors_list,
    keywords_list
FROM 
    FinalReport
LIMIT 100

SELECT COALESCE("t7"."MOVIE_ID", "t7"."MOVIE_ID") AS "MOVIE_ID", "t7"."TITLE", "t7"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t7"."CAST_COUNT", "t7"."ACTORS_LIST", "t7"."KEYWORDS_LIST"
FROM (SELECT "t5"."MOVIE_ID", "t5"."TITLE", "t5"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t5"."CAST_COUNT", "t5"."ACTORS_LIST", "t1"."KEYWORDS_LIST"
FROM (SELECT "movie_keyword"."movie_id" AS "MOVIE_ID", LISTAGG("keyword"."keyword", ', ') AS "KEYWORDS_LIST"
FROM "keyword"
INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "keyword"."id" = "movie_keyword"."keyword_id"
GROUP BY "movie_keyword"."movie_id") AS "t1"
RIGHT JOIN (SELECT MIN("t2"."id") AS "MOVIE_ID", "t2"."title" AS "TITLE", "t2"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", COUNT(DISTINCT "cast_info"."person_id") AS "CAST_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "s1"."name", ', ') AS "ACTORS_LIST"
FROM "complete_cast"
INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM "title"
WHERE "production_year" >= 2000) AS "t2" ON "complete_cast"."movie_id" = "t2"."id"
INNER JOIN ("s1" INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "s1"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id") ON "complete_cast"."subject_id" = "cast_info"."id"
GROUP BY "t2"."id", "t2"."title", "t2"."production_year") AS "t5" ON "t1"."MOVIE_ID" = "t5"."MOVIE_ID"
LIMIT 100) AS "t7"

SELECT COALESCE("id", "id") AS "id", "person_id", "movie_id", "person_role_id", "note", "nr_order", "role_id"
FROM "cast_info"

SELECT COALESCE("t7"."MOVIE_ID", "t7"."MOVIE_ID") AS "MOVIE_ID", "t7"."TITLE", "t7"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t7"."CAST_COUNT", "t7"."ACTORS_LIST", "t7"."KEYWORDS_LIST"
FROM (SELECT "t5"."MOVIE_ID", "t5"."TITLE", "t5"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t5"."CAST_COUNT", "t5"."ACTORS_LIST", "t1"."KEYWORDS_LIST"
FROM (SELECT "movie_keyword"."movie_id" AS "MOVIE_ID", LISTAGG("keyword"."keyword", ', ') AS "KEYWORDS_LIST"
FROM "keyword"
INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "keyword"."id" = "movie_keyword"."keyword_id"
GROUP BY "movie_keyword"."movie_id") AS "t1"
RIGHT JOIN (SELECT MIN("t2"."id") AS "MOVIE_ID", "t2"."title" AS "TITLE", "t2"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", COUNT(DISTINCT "s1"."person_id") AS "CAST_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "aka_name"."name", ', ') AS "ACTORS_LIST"
FROM "complete_cast"
INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM "title"
WHERE "production_year" >= 2000) AS "t2" ON "complete_cast"."movie_id" = "t2"."id"
INNER JOIN ("aka_name" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "s1"."person_id") ON "complete_cast"."subject_id" = "s1"."id"
GROUP BY "t2"."id", "t2"."title", "t2"."production_year") AS "t5" ON "t1"."MOVIE_ID" = "t5"."MOVIE_ID"
LIMIT 100) AS "t7"
